334 class Control
335 {
336 public:
337 Edu totalDur{};
338 Evpu totalWidth{};
339 Evpu minWidth{};
340 Evpu allotWidth{};
341
342 static const xml::XmlElementArray<Control>& xmlMappingArray();
343 };
344
345 // Populated only when the XML node includes a <control> element
346 std::shared_ptr<Control> control;
347
348 // Populated for standard beat entries (inci > 0)
349 Edu dur{};
350 Evpu pos{};
351 Evpu endPos{};
352 Evpu minPos{};
353
354 void integrityCheck() override
355 {
356 OthersBase::integrityCheck();
357 if (control && getInci() != 0) {
358 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Beat chart for measure " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has a control instance in inci " + std::to_string(*getInci()));
359 }
360 if (getInci() == 0 && !control) {
361 control = std::make_shared<Control>();
362 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Beat chart for measure " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " is missing its control instance.");
363 }
364 }
365
366 constexpr static std::string_view XmlNodeName = "beatChart";
367 static const xml::XmlElementArray<BeatChartElement>& xmlMappingArray();

516class FontDefinition : public OthersBase
517{
518 static constexpr uint32_t SYMBOL_CHARSET_MAC = 0xfff; // (4095)
519 static constexpr uint32_t SYMBOL_CHARSET_WIN = 2;
520
521public:
523 explicit FontDefinition(const DocumentWeakPtr& document, Cmper partId, ShareMode shareMode, Cmper cmper)
524 : OthersBase(document, partId, shareMode, cmper) {}
525
528 enum class CharacterSetBank
529 {
530 MacOS,
531 Windows
532 };
533
534 // Public properties corresponding to the XML structure
535 CharacterSetBank charsetBank{};
536 int charsetVal{};
541 int pitch{};
542 int family{};
543 std::string name;
544
558 bool calcIsSymbolFont() const
559 {
560 if (charsetBank == CharacterSetBank::MacOS && charsetVal == SYMBOL_CHARSET_MAC) {
561 return true;
562 }
563 if (charsetBank == CharacterSetBank::Windows && charsetVal == SYMBOL_CHARSET_WIN) {
564 return true;
565 }
566 return false;
567 }
568
569 constexpr static std::string_view XmlNodeName = "fontName";
570 static const xml::XmlElementArray<FontDefinition>& xmlMappingArray();
571};

584class Frame : public OthersBase
585{
586public:
588 explicit Frame(const DocumentWeakPtr& document, Cmper partId, ShareMode shareMode, Cmper cmper, Inci inci = 0)
589 : OthersBase(document, partId, shareMode, cmper, inci) {}
590
591 // Public properties corresponding to the XML structure
592 EntryNumber startEntry{};
593 EntryNumber endEntry{};
594 Edu startTime{};
595
598 void iterateRawEntries(std::function<bool(const std::shared_ptr<Entry>& entry)> iterator) const;
599
604 std::vector<std::shared_ptr<const Entry>> getEntries() const;
605
606 void integrityCheck() override
607 {
608 this->OthersBase::integrityCheck();
609 if (startTime && (startEntry || endEntry)) {
610 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Frame " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has non-zero startTime and non-zero startEntry or endEntry.");
611 }
612 if (!startTime && !startEntry) {
613 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Frame " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has no start entry.");
614 }
615 if (!startTime && !endEntry) {
616 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Frame " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has no end entry.");
617 }
618 }
619
620 constexpr static std::string_view XmlNodeName = "frameSpec";
621 static const xml::XmlElementArray<Frame>& xmlMappingArray();
622};

2563 void integrityCheck() override
2564 {
2565 OthersBase::integrityCheck();
2566 if (!staffLines && !customStaff) {
2567 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Staff or StaffStyle " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has neither a standard nor a custom staff definition.");
2568 } else if (staffLines && customStaff) {
2569 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Staff or StaffStyle " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has both a standard and a custom staff definition.");
2570 }
2571 if (customStaff) { // guarantee ascending order of staves.
2572 std::sort(customStaff.value().begin(), customStaff.value().end(),
2573 [](const auto& a, const auto& b) { return a < b; });
2574 }
2575 if (transposition) {
2576 if (!transposition->chromatic && !transposition->keysig) {
2577 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Staff or StaffStyle " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has transposition with neither keysig nor chromatic transposition defined.");
2578 } else if (transposition->chromatic && transposition->keysig) {
2579 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Staff or StaffStyle " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " has transposition with both keysig and chromatic transposition defined.");
2580 }
2581 }
2582 if (useNoteFont && !noteFont) {
2583 noteFont = std::make_shared<FontInfo>(getDocument()); // do this first to avoid unreachable code warning, since MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR might throw
2584 MUSX_INTEGRITY_ERROR("Staff or StaffStyle " + std::to_string(getCmper()) + " specifies to use a custom notehead font, but no custom font was provided.");
2585 }
2586 }
2587
2588 bool requireAllFields() const override { return false; }
2589

2591 static const xml::XmlElementArray<Staff>& xmlMappingArray();

2593private:
